    div.jumbotron.container
        div.jumbotron-header
            h1.display-l HAND-CRAFTED
            h2.display-m Web Sites
            h3.display-s From Scratch
        div.jumbotron-content
            p Hello! My name is Kenan, and I'm a Singapore-based web developer with strong computer science background.
            p I have a diverse set of skills, ranging from digital media marketing, web design, Jade + Sass + Javascript, all the way up to Ruby on Rails, Php and Java programming.
  section#portfolio
